Package de.hshl.obj.wavefront.mtl

All classes that have no other purpose than loading an MTL file.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MTL
    Represents a Material Library file.
    MTLParser
    The MTLParser collects predefined line parsers, which specify how each wavefront keyword should be interpreted.

Package de.hshl.obj.wavefront.mtl Description

All classes that have no other purpose than loading an MTL file. This excludes classes needed for OBJ files.
Author:
Johannes Vollmer
